  m_text: 'Welcome to `Twas the Buttler! In this game you play as a student at the
    detective academy. Each level is one of your practical exams. Solve all the cases,
    pass all your exams and graduate as a top tier detective!



    About Team The
    Buttlers:

    We are a small team of 6 University students from Saxion''s CMGT
    program:

    Kaloyan Dimov - Team Lead & Fullstack

    Bote Bouma - UI designer
    and Lead game designer

    Illia Vasylenko - Lead programmer

    Noah Mosselaar
    - Lead 3D artist

    Katleen Schaminee - 2D artist

    Fae - UI artist'
